CustomField.description: This field is optional. It is populated by a user or a data integration. It indicates the beneficial owner certifies it is an owner-documented FFI that is also a Trust without contingent or other unidentified beneficiaries, as prescribed by IRS forms W-8.
CustomField.inlineHelpText: Indicates the beneficial owner certifies it is an owner-documented FFI that is also a Trust without contingent or other unidentified beneficiaries, as prescribed by IRS forms W-8.
CustomField.label: Form W8 Owner Trust Indicator
